The leader of INRI Evangelical Spiritual Church, Primate Elijah Ayodele, has warned Ondo State Governor, Arakunrin Akeredolu that there is an underground plots to frustrate him out of the governorship race. He said that Akeredolu must restrategize and involve God if he wants to win the All Progressives Congress, APC, primary election because all his efforts will be frustrated, as “there will be a lot of kangaroo manipulation of election result,” he said in a statement to DAILY POST on Thursday. ‘’Akeredolu should sue for peace if he wants to contest under the platform of the APC because they want to destabilize him. “He should do everything within his power, otherwise they will manipulate and give it to Wale Oke.” He further stated that APC will break totally in 2023 if they don’t yield to the word of God and be prayerful. Ayodele said Nigeria will collapse if President Muhammadu Buhari fails to sack his service chiefs, saying they are no more relevant. “They should be relieved from their duties if not Nigeria will collapse security wise. “There will be more bandits attacks, kidnapping will be rampant and Nigeria will never get out of Boko Haram,” he said.